title: Catamaran Cruise
seo_title: Catamaran Cruise in Waikiki | Things to do in Waikiki
seo_description: One of the best ways to see views of the majestic Diamond Head is from a catamaran. Make your Hawaii Holiday even more memorable with a Catamaran Cruise!
contents_1: One of the best views of the majestic Diamond Head is from catamaran at sunset.
description: One of the best ways to see views of the majestic Diamond Head is from a catamaran. Relax on a sunset cruise and take in the spectacular scenery of Waikiki.
